Shittybot
=========
A fork of Sam Stephenson's excellent smeggdrop.
No longer requires eggdrop

Requirements:
- Perl
  - POE::Component::IRC::State
  - Tcl
  - Moose
  - Time::Out
  - Carp::Always
  - Data::Dump
  - Config::General
  - POE::Component::SSLify - if you want SSL
- Tcl 8.4
  - tcllib
- Git

Installation:
- Check out
- Edit bot.conf
- Run 'run-bot'
